All3Media Up for Sale for as Much as $1.2 Billion, FT Reports

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-04-01T05:24:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-01/all3media-up-for-sale-for-as-much-as-1-2-billion-ft-reports.html
All3Media Worldwide Ltd., a U.K.
television production company of which buyout firm Permira LLP
owns a little more than half and management 40 percent,
appointed UBS AG to carry out a review that may result in a sale
of the business for 600 million to 750 million pounds ($960
million to $1.2 billion), the Financial Times reported, citing
two unidentified people familiar with the matter.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in  London  on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 